<h2>Gum sores, Tenderness to touch and White patches inside mouth</h2>
<p>WebMD Symptom Checker helps you find the most common medical conditions indicated by the symptoms gum sores, tenderness to touch and white patches inside mouth including Thrush (infants and children), Toothbrush irritation, and Hematoma.</p>
